OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy rain
OL,6,Fwill sweep east across the region this
OL,7,Fevening accompanied by strong to gale
OL,8,Fsouth or southwest winds. Clearer for
OL,9,Fa time tonight then blustery showers
OL,10,Fsetting in.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with
OL,13,Ffrequent blustery showers and gale
OL,14,Fforce winds. A brighter afternoon with
OL,15,Fsome sunny intervals but still some
OL,16,Fshowers. Winds slowly easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
