OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain then blustery showers on
OL,7,FThursday, gales. Colder with sunshine
OL,8,Fand showers on Friday, snow on high
OL,9,Fground. Remaining showery on Saturday.
